.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH gdrivesync 1  "gdrivesync 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
gdrivesync \- Google Drive sync — CLI (talks to gds\-daemon via D\-Bus)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBgdrivesync\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Google Drive sync — CLI (talks to gds\-daemon via D\-Bus)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Machine\-readable JSON on stdout (stable field names)
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress non\-error stdout
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Extra diagnostics (implies info\-level logging if RUST_LOG unset)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
gdrivesync\-status(1)
Per\-account status, quota, last sync (requires running daemon)
.TP
gdrivesync\-accounts(1)
.TP
gdrivesync\-sync(1)
.TP
gdrivesync\-folders(1)
.TP
gdrivesync\-errors(1)
Recent sync errors from daemon DB
.TP
gdrivesync\-quota(1)
Drive storage quota per account
.TP
gdrivesync\-daemon(1)
.TP
gdrivesync\-completions(1)
Print shell completions (bash, zsh, fish)
.TP
gdrivesync\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
